title: This TV Couple’s Wedding Photos Are Straight Out Of A Fairytale
text:
Swagata Dam Feb . 27 . 2017 
Dil Dosti Dance actress Vrinda Dawda tied the knot with her beau Bhavin Mehta in December 2016. And today, I happened to stumble upon some really spectacular pre-wedding and wedding photos of their wedding. And since I know how much you guys dig celebrity shaadis , I decided to compile them for you. Check these out. ‹ ›
